# Mobile UI Skill

## Objective
Create responsive mobile-first interfaces optimized for touch interaction.

## Design Rules
- Mobile-first layout mandatory
- Minimum touch target: 48px
- Thumb-friendly navigation
- Bottom tab navigation preferred
- Avoid desktop-style layouts

## UI Standards
- Consistent spacing system
- Reusable components
- Skeleton loading states
- Smooth transitions

## Components
- Cards
- Lists
- Forms
- Modal sheets
- Floating actions

## UX Principles
- Reduce user steps
- Clear feedback after action
- Visible loading indicators
